#. type: Plain text
#: R-admin.texi:1226
msgid ""
"Set the environment variable @env{TMPDIR} to the absolute path to a writable "
"directory, with a path specified with forward slashes and no spaces.  (The "
"default is @file{/tmp}, which may not be useful on Windows.)"
