"@code{CFLAGS}, @code{CPPFLAGS}, @code{FFLAGS}, @code{CXXFLAGS} and "
"@code{LIBS} in @code{R_XTRA_CFLAGS} (and so on).  These are for options "
"which are always required, for example to force @acronym{IEC}@tie{}60559 "
